      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "It sounds like you are going through a truly painful and isolating time, and I hear how much suffering you are in. Please know that these feelings of being trapped and exhausted are heavy burdens to carry alone. If you are feeling overwhelmed, reaching out to a doctor or a mental health professional can provide you with support and options for managing these difficult symptoms. You don't have to face this feeling of being stuck by yourself.",
